<div id="post-441406" class="blog-post position-7 odd-post"><div class="odd-post-inner blog-post-inner"><h1 class="title"><a href="http://softwarelivre.org/libreoffice/blog/tdf-infographics-may-2012">TDF InfoGraphics, May 2012</a></h1><span class="publishing-info"><span class="date">10 de Junho de 2012, 0:00</span><span class="author">, por Software Livre Brasil</span><span class="comments"> - <a href="/libreoffice/blog/tdf-infographics-may-2012#comments_list"><span class='comment-count hide'>0</span><span class='comment-count-write-out'>sem comentários ainda</span></a></span></span><p><img title="TDF InfoGraphics June 2012.jpg" src="http://documentfoundation.files.wordpress.com/2012/06/tdf-infographics-june-2012.jpg?w=900&amp;h=1391" border="0" height="1391" alt="TDF InfoGraphics June 2012" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" width="900"></p>
<p>If you are a LibreOffice user, you can download the Hybrid PDF from <a href="http://www.italovignoli.org/uploads/tdf-infographics1206.pdf">here</a> and open it as a normal ODF file (using File &gt; Open). If you are not a LibreOffice user, you can open the file using a PDF viewer, or install <a href="http://www.libreoffice.org/download/">LibreOffice</a> to discover this unique feature.</p>
<br>  <a href="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gocomments/documentfoundation.wordpress.com/1110/"><img src="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/comments/documentfoundation.wordpress.com/1110/" border="0" alt=""></a> <a href="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/godelicious/documentfoundation.wordpress.com/1110/"><img src="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/delicious/documentfoundation.wordpress.com/1110/" border="0" alt=""></a> <a href="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gofacebook/documentfoundation.wordpress.com/1110/"><img src="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/facebook/documentfoundation.wordpress.com/1110/" border="0" alt=""></a> <a href="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gotwitter/documentfoundation.wordpress.com/1110/"><img src="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/twitter/documentfoundation.wordpress.com/1110/" border="0" alt=""></a> <a href="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gostumble/documentfoundation.wordpress.com/1110/"><img src="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/stumble/documentfoundation.wordpress.com/1110/" border="0" alt=""></a> <a href="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/godigg/documentfoundation.wordpress.com/1110/"><img src="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/digg/documentfoundation.wordpress.com/1110/" border="0" alt=""></a> <a href="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/goreddit/documentfoundation.wordpress.com/1110/"><img src="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/reddit/documentfoundation.wordpress.com/1110/" border="0" alt=""></a> <img src="http://stats.wordpress.com/b.gif?host=blog.documentfoundation.org&amp;#038;blog=17531842&amp;#038;post=1110&amp;#038;subd=documentfoundation&amp;#038;ref=&amp;#038;feed=1" border="0" height="1" alt="" width="1"><br style="clear:both"/></div></div>
